descriptionHtml:
Video Compress is a real video Compress, which supports almost all video format; HD video, HTML5 video, WMV, MKV, AVI, MP4,MOV.

Video Compress has a number of basic editing settings. With these you can customize the video size and aspect ratio and extract audio and video from files. Overall, Video Compress's basic conversion function is quick and easy

If you have large size of video and a memory issue then you can compress size of your video.

Use it to reduce data usage. Compressing a video makes it much easier to share on social networks such as facebook , google + , whatsapp , etc

Key features:

- Supports MP4, FLV, MPEG-1,2, MOV, MKV, WMV, AVI, VOB, 3GP, SWF, MP3, AAC, WAV, and more
- Fully Customize video parameters based on requirments so produced best output result.
- Display fully detailed video information
- Video converting speed is fast for all videos
- Remain best video quality after converting video
- Simple, user friendly and eye catching design
- Saves edited files within app
- Easy user interface
- Totally free app
